x4freetext: Natural Sm foils with 23.13 um, 24.20 um and 25.14 um
irradiation technique and high resolution gamma
spectrometry were used. SM metalic foils, interleaved
with Al foils for monitoring beam characteristics
were stacked and irradiated at the UCL (LLN)
Each foil activity was measured 4 times.
Al and Ti monitors were used.
